title: Episode 7
description:
The boys fly solo this week, talking about the latest Sway House drama, why Bryce is still mad at Dave, and the Jay Alvarez sextape. Dave and Josh also do their best at identifying some feminine products, and picking out the Sway Boys by their abs.
